# Metric Resource: Synonyms
<https://w3id.org/soel/metric/Synonyms> a dqv:Metric ;

    dcterms:identifier "https://w3id.org/soel/metric/Synonyms" ;
    dcterms:title "Exact match against WordNet synonym relations"@en ;
    rdfs:label "Synonyms: Exact match against WordNet synonym relations"^^xsd:string ;
    vivo:abbreviation "synonyms"^^xsd:string ;
    dcat:version "0.0.1"^^xsd:string ;
    ftr:status "Active"@en ;
    dcat:landingPage <https://w3id.org/soel/metric/Synonyms> ;

    # Descriptive Content
    dcterms:description """
This metric aims to evaluate if the generated label and all of its corresponding synonyms if is the exact match to the gold standard ontology.

**Calculation Process:**

1. Get all synonyms of the generated label from the WordNet dataset as generated label set.

2. Matching all labels in generate label set with labels from the gold standard ontology.

3. If there is a perfect match, the result is 1; otherwise, the result is 0.

**Example:** 

Generated_label: Wine

Generated_label_set: Wine, alcohol, vintage, red_wine, white_wine, dark_red, ..., etc.

Gold_standard_label: red_wine

Result: 

Synonyms(Gold_standard_label, Generated_label_set) = 1

**What is being measured?**

This metric identifies semantically equivalent concepts expressed through different lexical forms by utlizing the synonym relation of the WordNet or other lexical dictionary.
""" ;
    dcat:keyword "Ontology Concept Matching"@en ;
    dcat:keyword "Metric"@en ;
    dcat:keyword "Classes"@en ;
    
    # Relationships and Provenance
    dpv:isApplicableFor <https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q184754> ;
    ftr:hasBenchmark <https://w3id.org/soel/benchmark/ALL> ;
    <http://semanticscience.org/resource/SIO_000234> <https://w3id.org/soel/test/Synonyms> ; # Has Implementation
    ftr:supportedBy <https://w3id.org/soel/> ;
    dqv:inDimension  "Ontology Engineering"^^xsd:string ;
    
    # Provenance
    dcterms:creator <https://orcid.org/0009-0001-9475-8159> ;
    dcat:contactPoint <https://orcid.org/0009-0001-9475-8159> ;
    dcterms:publisher <https://oeg.fi.upm.es> ;
    dcterms:publisher <https://ror.org/03n6nwv02> ;
